Node.Notes: Precise meaning uncertain. One area around success/good result and another area around sound wisdom/prudence.
"Walk in" followed by abstract noun "blameless" means to live/conduct oneself in a blameless way/in integrity.

The learner of wisdom will understand three conjoined qualities of "righteousness," "justice," and "equity," and a fourth element "every good path" (probably includes the first three and goes beyond them).
Uncertain. Tree assumes progressive descriptions of only one generic group of women in 2:16 and 2:17, so the strange woman is not a foreigner, but another man’s wife.
